> ⚠
> 
> * The loading screen does **not** end by itself and absolutely needs a call to [endLoadingScreen](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/endLoadingScreen) command
> 
> * Game simulation is disabled during Loading Screen operation (at least in single player):
> 
> * do **not** use the [sleep](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/sleep) command between startLoadingScreen and [endLoadingScreen](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/endLoadingScreen) as **it may freeze the game** - use [uiSleep](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/uiSleep) instead
> 
> * [waitUntil](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/waitUntil) *can* be used to wait for variable initialisation or script loading
> [](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/Category:Arma_3)Use [BIS_fnc_startLoadingScreen](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/BIS_fnc_startLoadingScreen) to prevent potential usage conflicts.

examples:
