	[[[sin](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/sin) _r, -[sin](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/sin) _p, [cos](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/cos) _r * [cos](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/cos) _p], -_y] [call](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/call) [BIS_fnc_rotateVector2D](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/BIS_fnc_rotateVector2D)
