};

[systemChat](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/systemChat) [str](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/str) [count](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/count) _string;		*// 6 - outer scope is affected by forceUnicode as well, because the command mode is 0*

forceUnicode -1; *// cancelled*

[call](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/call) {
	[systemChat](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/systemChat) [str](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/str) [count](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/count) _string;	*// 12 - wrong count*
	forceUnicode 1;
	[systemChat](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/systemChat) [str](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/str) [count](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/count) _string;	*// 6 - correct result, but Unicode it reset after this operation, because command mode is 1*
};

[systemChat](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/systemChat) [str](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/str) [count](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/count) _string;		*// 12 - outer scope is not affected as it was reset right after [count](https://community.bistudio.com/wiki/count)*
